{"tid":1164711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係得trump trump熟六國論","createTime":"2019-05-21T10:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T09:50:30.000Z","uid":74778,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"19ee9d7702d954859b6e8f4be8eb8316ab7838fe","tid":1164711,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"根本個個團體企業商人甚至聯合國，都知道中國市場大，唔敢得失共產黨。個個都知共產黨係仆街黎嫁啦，行入世界舞台根本係爛仔格，劣幣驅良幣，由附近小國開始，因為怕左佢而同佢行埋，最後小國政府就會因為不斷出賣自己國家對中國既依賴，貪心的小狗咁比共產黨食撚埋，例子就係一帶一路d戇鳩國家<br />\n<br />\n宜家德國法國意大利甚至英國呢d傳統歐洲大國，都話唔想放棄大陸市場，為左市場，縱容共產黨呢d爛仔行為，活生生咁睇到劣幣驅良幣係點縱出黎。好似泰國要吞六國既決心咁，縱到大撚曬<br />\n<br />\n羅家英Only you.gif，得Trump trump，bright knight<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZTNjsNc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZTNjsNc.png&h=2a4f1b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n知道六國破滅非兵不利戰不善 斃在賂泰。前車可鑑，賂黎都無用，共產黨同你白紙黑字都走你數，你諗住賂完佢同你講人情？揸揸手做朋友？咪癲。根本唔賂佢，齊心杯佢，佢根本只可以單機打飛機食樹皮。仲偷到人野？仲有機會走人數？無，根本食飽飯既機會都無。<br />\n<br />\nTrump trump宜家做既就係帶頭杯共產黨"},{"pid":"1b57c25bc16d04d0172508334b5bafd320c17874","tid":1164711,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T10:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcaeca2f144419d5ffd68eab1f9f8e16a3be77a","tid":1164711,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6797c70cad4933668eba58ac652176dc65ac3856","tid":1164711,"uid":55953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:37:19.000Z","msg":"AGGER"},{"pid":"91f4aa3c1c073c3b8cbcf1d619d08322b8ac0ae8","tid":1164711,"uid":101049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:42:13.000Z","msg":"Trump is the trump of the USA.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d00d17208443ced12e31308f4c77354734121be","tid":1164711,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:43:53.000Z","msg":"美加帶頭，用華為開刀，日韓宜家都無論係巿場上定原材料上都杯華為，華為只能同外交部一樣死剩把口"},{"pid":"d739c573ce24635a1aa7f3e145d0abc2b3aa76a4","tid":1164711,"uid":244332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"President Xi is my friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1dbf613dca461c037a90eaf2aaab8f75b102d8","tid":1164711,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d739c573ce24635a1aa7f3e145d0abc2b3aa76a4","tid":1164711,"uid":244332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"President Xi is my friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"侵侵：朋友要黎出賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89b98799fed39179c83e4f58d66caf168f93167","tid":1164711,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"秦國變泰國<br />\n泰國變秦國<br />\n好亂"}]}